class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-72c75dc2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"72c75dc2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Global Agricultural Intelligence Map\n<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6bb61d0c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6bb61d0c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Explore real-time agricultural data, market trends, and country-level insights across more than 190 countries. The IFU Global Agricultural Intelligence Map transforms complex data into a simple, interactive experience\u2014allowing users to quickly understand production levels, trade flows, climate conditions, and investment opportunities worldwide.<\/p><p><strong>How it benefits you:<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><strong>Make informed decisions faster<\/strong>\u00a0with access to reliable, up-to-date agricultural intelligence<\/li><li><strong>Identify market opportunities<\/strong>\u00a0by exploring supply, demand, and pricing trends by country<\/li><li><strong>Discover partnerships<\/strong>\u00a0by locating active cooperatives, farmers, and stakeholders globally<\/li><li><strong>Access deeper insights instantly<\/strong>\u2014click any country to unlock detailed dashboards, reports, and analytics powered by the IFU Data Engine<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-50f7b7da e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"50f7b7da\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" id=\"world-map\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e03655d